类 BudgetDataContainer

java.lang.Object
Model.BudgetDataContainer
public class BudgetDataContainer extends Object
Represents a container for budget-related data in the Smart Finance Application. This class encapsulates budget recommendations, monthly financial summaries, top spending categories, significant consumption details, and custom budget settings for a user.
版本:
1.0
作者:
Group 19
